{"tid":1848530,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"冇人陪唔敢罷？你入左工會未先:o)？","createTime":"2020-01-28T13:33:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T13:47:21.000Z","uid":51171,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cc98bff29632d195adef10f057f033861452c2bd","tid":1848530,"uid":51171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:33:16.000Z","msg":"唔係得醫護有power反鳩佢枱，<br />\n其實每一行、每個打工仔都有power。<br />\n<br />\n成日話「手停口停，冇人陪唔敢罷」，<br />\n問心，唔一黎就話罷喇，你行左第一步未先(i.e.自己加入工會、搵相同立場嘅同事陪你一齊入)？<br />\n<br />\n定係你原地踏步乜都冇做過？<br />\n然後人地一召喚罷工就叫春：囚徒困境、自己一個唔敢....<br />\n<br />\nbtw，工會日後仲可以幫到你爭取其他勞工權益(薪金、福利...)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">行多一步，唔好咁懶</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd62d4446a7435f557f95235db96e8f7a36913d6","tid":1848530,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:34:45.000Z","msg":"入ed"},{"pid":"6e41934e38ddf3210fd563d615a34ace9b37d9dd","tid":1848530,"uid":51171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd62d4446a7435f557f95235db96e8f7a36913d6","tid":1848530,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:34:45.000Z","msg":"入ed"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:37:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79249222caaba13741d2a91b1120f6e52c45a130","tid":1848530,"uid":51171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:43:54.000Z","msg":"是咪應該開喺時事台"},{"pid":"3516f99ce06279fafdf30d4e3075cd06b1f91b6f","tid":1848530,"uid":301139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:47:21.000Z","msg":"有冇人放link係下面<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"